<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Your School ERP Account Credentials</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #292648;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .credentials {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #292648;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to School ERP</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello,</p>
        
        <p>Your account has been created in the School ERP system. Below are your login credentials:</p>
        
        <div class="credentials">
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
            <p><strong>Password:</strong> {{password}}</p>
            <p><strong>Role:</strong> {{role}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Please use these credentials to log in to the system. We recommend changing your password after your first login.</p>
        
        <p>
            <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Login to School ERP</a>
        </p>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact the school administration.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 